OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Ffine end to the day and staying dry
OL,7,Fand mainly clear overnight. Occasional
OL,8,Flow cloud may filter through from the
OL,9,Feast. Winds remaining light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,12,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,13,Fsunny spells developing. Temperatures
OL,14,Fdown a bit, but still warm or very
OL,15,Fwarm in any sunshine. Light northerly
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
