OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled, although a little
OL,7,Fearly light rain or drizzle possible
OL,8,Fover the hills. Cloudy or bright with
OL,9,Fsunny spells developing. Feeling warm
OL,10,Fin any sunshine.
